Description: Home Buyer
Full Description: We love helping Buffalo home buyers and sellers! We’ve been in real estate for several years and we’ve found that we can help you a lot more by buying your house directly from you than we can by going through some big company. This is why we started Liberty Home Buyers! We’re a family-owned business and focus on helping homeowners like you find solutions for your problem whether you’re going through a foreclosure, can’t sell your property, or just need to sell their house for all kinds of reasons. We work with sellers who would like to sell their house quickly without the hassle of listing with an agent, and having countless showings – and who agree to taking a monthly payment. We can close quickly, and you can have the peace of mind that your house is sold, and you don’t even have to be out of the house as soon as we close. We usually pay all of the closing costs, which are several thousand dollars in New York State, so you wouldn’t have to come to closing with a nickel. We often are able to pay full price for your home, and we close everything with an attorney when your ready. We will take your house as-is which means no home inspector is going to come pick your house apart, which can be costly. Most importantly, you’ll find when you sell to us – you’ll net more money than any other way you can sell, because there is no commission and we usually pay all of the closing costs. Over the years we have been able to help lots of other local families sell they homes quickly and without any of the headaches of selling your house by yourself or listing with an agent, and we can help you too. Just contact us today so you can start getting the help that you need to get the deal that you want!

Full Description: C Schreiber LLC provides CISO coaching services to help universities simplify and improve their cybersecurity strategy. Chris Schreiber is a higher education cybersecurity expert with more than two decades experience supporting institutions of all sizes. His prior roles included serving as CISO at the University of Chicago, the University of Arizona, and University of Wisconsin-Whitewater. In addition to university leadership roles, Chris has supported numerous higher education clients while working for international technology companies. At SunGard Higher Education (now Ellucian) he built new managed security services used by dozens of colleges and universities. More recently, he helped universities around the world transform their information security programs as a cybersecurity strategist with FireEye. This varied experience in both campus and industry leadership roles has given him a deep understanding about how information security can be improved at higher education institutions. He shares this experience with clients from his home in Tucson, AZ. Chris has a Masters Certificate in Project Management from University of Wisconsin – Madison and a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration from Central Michigan University. He also holds multiple professional certifications, including Certified Information Security Manager (CISM) and Project Management Professional (PMP).

Description: Best Medical Billing And Coding Service For You Medical billing and coding are two critical components of the healthcare industry
Full Description: Best Medical Billing And Coding Service For You Medical billing and coding are two critical components of the healthcare industry that ensure healthcare providers are compensated for the services they render. These two practices work hand-in-hand to facilitate the reimbursement process, translating medical procedures into numeric or alphanumeric codes and processing insurance claims for healthcare services. Medical Coding Medical coding is a fundamental aspect of healthcare that plays a vital role in the billing and reimbursement process. It involves the translation of medical procedures, diagnoses, and treatments into a standardized code format that can be easily understood by healthcare providers, insurance companies, and government agencies. The process of medical coding begins with a patient's visit to a healthcare provider. During this visit, the provider takes note of the patient's symptoms, performs various tests, and makes a diagnosis. The provider then prescribes a course of treatment, which may include medication, physical therapy, or surgery.

Description: FITBLOX is a health, fitness, and social DApp built on the EOS blockchain, combining incentive-based rewards and social media monetization.
Full Description: Executive Summary At FITBLOX we are revolutionizing the health and fitness industries by creating a stake-weighted, incentive-based social experience that rewards and monetizes inspired behavior. By leveraging the inherent benefits of distributed ledger technology; we'll provide a safe, secure, and private medium of exchange between fitness enthusiasts and strategic partners within our purpose-built decentralized ecosystem. FITBLOX will provide support for and access to an array of health and fitness-centric goods, services, and programs by utilizing our strategic partnership network. Users will enjoy community building, a nurturing learning environment, as well as a forum where users are the star of your own fitness journey. Unlike centralized fitness tracking applications and social media networks, with FITBLOX, you're always in control of your identity, your data, and most importantly your health.  FITBLOX will disrupt the fitness industry by building an industry leading Fitness Tracking DApp (Decentralized Application) that will store user data and content on a secure blockchain, protecting FITBLOX users from the vulnerability of centralized data repositories. The FITBLOX DApp will empower users to create additional income stream while doing something they love in a healthy, positive way by interacting with and mentoring others with like-minded goals.  FITBLOX will utilize a unique stake-weighted voting system which will encourage users to grow their voting/rewards power and encourage participation in our motivational user advancement model. FITBLOX is a health, fitness and social community rewards platform powered by our revolutionary decentralized fitness application - the FITBLOX DApp. FITBLOX will enable users to own, protect, and control their own data and content on the EOS decentralized blockchain.  FITBLOX combines secure fitness tracking; user monetized social media, and an incentive-based stake weighted motivational rewards paradigm.
